be a multilinear map between finite-dimensional vector spaces, where formula_20 has dimension formula_21, and formula_22 has dimension formula_23. If we choose a basis formula_24 for each formula_20 and a basis formula_26 for formula_22 (using bold for vectors), then we can define a collection of scalars formula_28 by

:formula_29

Then the scalars formula_30 completely determine the multilinear function formula_31. In particular, if

